    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You release an explosion of wind protecting you with a burst of air. Until the start of your next turn, you have a +4 Bonus to AC including the triggering attack. Creatures who are within 10ft. of you when you cast this jutsu must succeed a Strength saving throw, taking 2d6 wind damage and push to the edge of this jutsu's radius into a space that can hold them on a fail.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the radius by 5 feet.</p>",
